      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/argentina-milei-tears-down-symbols-of-peronism-to-woo-foreign-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈维尔·麦利（Javier Milei）试图在阿根廷重新品牌的自由市场天堂重新品牌时，试图消除阿根廷占主导地位的佩隆主义的每一个遗迹。]]></description>
