      <title>监管机构说，瑞银投资银行上限将受到欢迎</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/finma-ceo-says-he-d-welcome-limit-to-ubs-investment-bank-size</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士金融监管机构的负责人表示，他赞成瑞银集团（UBS Group AG）提出的限制其投资银行规模的提议，这表明在有关该国最大贷方的未来资本需求的辩论中，潜在的前进方向。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/finma-ceo-says-he-d-welcome-limit-to-ubs-investment-bank-size</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 08:23:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着贸易战的要求，亚洲天然气跌至一年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/asian-gas-falls-to-one-year-low-as-trade-war-stokes-demand-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球贸易战威胁要击中该地区最大的经济体并缓慢对燃料需求缓慢，因此亚洲液化的天然气价格下降了将近一年的最低水价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-08/asian-gas-falls-to-one-year-low-as-trade-war-stokes-demand-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 08 Apr 2025 05:57:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
